So US companies buy and resell Chinese products at much higher prices paying very little to the actual producers of the goods. As a result only a small part of the income goes to Chinese companies. You as a product seller get following benefits: ‚Ä¢ Access to premium TV inventory in real time ‚Ä¢ Combine the power of digital audience targeting with the reach of TV ‚Ä¢ Reach users with relevant, meaningful and engaging messages. ‚Ä¢ Eliminate waste with better insights to plan and optimize campaigns  Use Engagement Tokens to access unique distribution channels for your products in the United States and build a reputable business with EGT bounty program.  Watch the full video to get more info: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZlUABqFkA1w   More about our offer for the Chinese market: Engagement Token has partnered with Futures Media, whose technology bridges the gap between the automated advertising buying platforms and television sellers of inventory.
